HandyJORM.query

Class BaseSoftQueryState<T extends BaseModel>

  • java.lang.Object
    • HandyJORM.query.BaseSoftQueryState<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SoftQueryFromState, SoftQueryJoinState, SoftQueryOrderByState, SoftQuerySelectState, SoftQueryWhereState

    public abstract class BaseSoftQueryState<T extends BaseModel>
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by DeiGray on 11/05/2017. The Base to create a SoftQueryState. Each SoftQueryState represent a "state", a part of a SQL Select query.
